commits.message: Fixed audio playback in chromium. Cleaned up sound service code.

Changed the way gain works and added a compressor to make the volume loud and consistent while eliminating clipping and popping. Also made it hide zero-value tx by default and not play sounds for zeroes while they are hidden.
